      <h5>PLAYGEN - Playlist Generator App</h5>
      <p>My first attempt at an app, created in week 2 of the course in conjunction with <a href="https://github.com/DeadFred121">Fred Cliff</a>.  PLAYGEN is a ruby terminal app that allows a user to add, delete and show songs in their playlist that they have created, and also has features to find song lyrics and artist information with the help of Ruby gems.  <a href="https://github.com/calebharnell/Playlist-App">Link to GitHub</a></p>
